### Get root
GET http://localhost:8787/

### Get projects
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects

### Get one project
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/1

### Get non-existent project
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/999

### Get invalid ID
GET http://localhost:8787/api/projects/abc

### Valid create
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test Project",
  "description": "A description"
}

### Missing name
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "No name"
}

### Unknown field
POST http://localhost:8787/api/projects
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Valid",
  "unknownField": "bad"
}